<p style="padding-left: 30px;">2. One (1) digital copy of your passport (For Foreigners)</p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">3. One (1) digital copy of your Citizen ID (For Thai Citizens only)</p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">4. One (1) digital copy of your of Residence Registration (For Thai Citizens only)</p>
