<p style="padding-left: 30px;">7. One (1) digital copy of your brief CV or Resume</p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">8. One (1) digital copy of your Research Concept Paper (CP) (2-3 Pages)</p>
<ul>
<li>After uploading 1-8 please pay interview fee- (2000 Baht) if you transfer Thai currency through a bank in Thailand and approximately (US$110) if you transfer from overseas banks. Then send a copy of receipt or transfer slip to:<a href="mailto:phdelm@au.edu"> Phdelm@au.edu</a></li>
<li>As soon as the tasks mentioned above are taken care you will be informed about face-to-face or online interview which will be held using any of the popular conferencing tools such as WebEx, Skype, Facebook Messenger or any other VDO conferencing tool you may be using. Your admission will be finalized within one week after you complete all requirements and an official Admission Letter will be sent to you.</li>
<li>Thank you for applying at GSeL. We are very pleased that you will study with one of the best international university in Thailand, ASEAN and beyond. Welcome aboard.</li>
</ul>
